law.history: Repealed 2004 Ky. Acts ch 59, sec. 17, effective July 13, 2004. -- Created 2000 Ky. Acts ch. 521, sec. 13, effective July 14, 2000.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Prohibition against contract requiring mandatory use of hospitalist.
metadata.lrc-note: (7/14/2000). This section was originally assigned the KRS number 304.17A-532 in the Acts disposition table for the 2000 Kentucky Acts, but the number assignment was altered in codification.
